com.google.cloud.firestore

Class WriteBatch

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.cloud.firestore.WriteBatch

  • public class WriteBatch
extends Object
    A Firestore WriteBatch that can be used to atomically commit multiple write operations at once.
    See Also:
    Firestore.batch()
